    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer it to a clean board and shred it apart using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Remove the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong> from the pan and discard</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken </strong>to the pan with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> pulled chicken pie filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
