    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>pulled chicken pie filling</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>and top evenly with the <strong>creamy mash</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 12-15 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>tomato & pulled free range chicken thigh potato-topped pie</strong></p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Once the pie is nearly ready, add the <strong>blanched peas </strong>to a colander and pour plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>all over them until they're warmed through</p>",
